description: This NY mac n cheese truck is rollin' out all the stops with their gourmet menu. One favorite menu item is their pulled pork mac n cheese made with slow roasted pulled pork, house made bbq, pickled jalapeños and rosemary scented bread. Be sure to also try their lobster mac n cheese with maine lobster and sherry shallots, and of course their classic mac n cheese - a cheddar and gruyere blend.
name: Macarollin'
